{"tid":433211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大廈保安員聞巨響　揭老翁墮樓亡","createTime":"2017-10-12T07:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T09:37:14.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e4f8df4eb18e0f17dc70da3fa23037f7fe957afa","tid":433211,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171012/large/1507789305_3ab8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171012%2Flarge%2F1507789305_3ab8.jpg&h=01151819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中午12時45分，油麻地庇利金街45號利金大樓，保安員聽到天井傳來一聲巨響，查看下見到有鞋和衣物在簷篷上，懷疑有人從高處墮下，於是報警。消防員接報到場，由鄰廈天台游繩落去天井，個多小時後救起一名老翁，但救護員證實老翁當場傷重死亡，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"2d9ec0d1111e72dbcfcc688b0d67c23a492b7207","tid":433211,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:59:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57322564&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57322564%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171012&d=zxSEwzIAsp08fc7Qcb1rKcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=223037ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57322564%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171012&h=8c866f95\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57322564&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171012</a>"},{"pid":"6d47ccafada94354efdd125afdfb8f4de3feab7e","tid":433211,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-